eiθ=cos⁡θ+isin⁡θeiπ=−1+0=−1

% write code here 
\begin{align}
	e^{i\theta}
		&= \cos{\theta} + i\sin{\theta} \\
	e^{i\pi}
		&= -1 + 0 \\
		&= -1
\end{align}
